description: T3809, T3814, T3816, T3817, T3818, T3820, T3823, T3824, T3825 and T3826 (Lombardy Poplars) - fell and replace. (Summary).
decision_conditions: The submitted arboricultural report does not provide an accurate current indication of the condition of the trees T3809, T3814, T3816, T3817, T3818, T3820, T3823, T3824, T3825 and T3826 (Lombardy Poplars). As there is insufficient justification for the removal of these trees and the collective contribution they provide to the visual amenity of the local area, a Tree Preservation Order is being sought for their protection
application_type_full: Tree works: Trees in conservation areas/subject to TPOs
